		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />To change some sound playback code to use "virtual" sound registers, use a good NES debugger, like FCEUXDSP.
<br />Just set breakpoints on writes to sound registers, then modify the address of the sound writes to point to the 'virtual' sound registers instead.

		

