<br />I originally wanted to put the Sound RAM registers from a disassembled ''Hebereke.NSF'' into different slots. like putting $6700-68ff to 6700-68FF and $0080-$07FF to 6080-60FF. And since I am using SMB1, I am going to delete the sound and music code and data for the code to work
<br />
<br />But there is one problem for the sound RAM: Registers only go to $0000 to $07FF. and it does not work there.
<br />
<br />Does anyone know what is going on with the original plan?

		

